{  
   "content":"Meditating among liars,",
   "children":[  
      {  
         "content":"and retreating sternly into myself,"
      },
      {  
         "content":"indifferent of lies or the truth?",
         "children":[  
            {  
               "content":"O ME, man of slack faith so long!",
               "children":[  
                  {  
                     "content":"Standing aloof--",
                     "children":[  
                        {  
                           "content":"all-diffused truth;"
                        }
                     ]
                  },
                  {  
                     "content":"Discovering to-day there is no lie,",
                     "children":[  
                        {  
                           "content":"or form of lie,"
                        }
                     ]
                  },
                  {  
                     "content":"And that each thing exactly represents itself",
                     "children":[  
                        {  
                           "content":"and what has preceded  it,"
                        }
                     ]
                  },
                  {  
                     "content":"And that the truth includes all,",
                     "children":[  
                        {  
                           "content":"and is compact,",
                           "children":[  
                              {  
                                 "content":"just as much as space is compact,"
                              }
                           ]
                        }
                     ]
                  }
               ]
            },
            {  
               "content":"Only aware to-day of compact,",
               "children":[  
                  {  
                     "content":"denying portions so long;"
                  },
                  {  
                     "content":"Or as any law of the earth,",
                     "children":[  
                        {  
                           "content":"or any natural production of the earth does."
                        }
                     ]
                  },
                  {  
                     "content":"And that there is no flaw or vacuum in the amount of the truth--",
                     "children":[  
                        {  
                           "content":"but that all is truth without exception;"
                        }
                     ]
                  },
                  {  
                     "content":"I feel in myself that I represent falsehoods equally with the rest,"
                  }
               ]
            },
            {  
               "content":"I see",
               "children":[  
                  {  
                     "content":"that there are really no liars or lies after all,",
                     "children":[  
                        {  
                           "content":"Is it upon the ground, or in water or fire?",
                           "children":[  
                              {  
                                 "content":"or in the spirit of man?",
                                 "children":[  
                                    {  
                                       "content":"or in the meat and blood?",
                                       "children":[  
                                          {  
                                             "content":"(This is curious, and may not be realized immediately--)",
                                             "children":[  
                                                {  
                                                   "content":"(But it must be  realized;)",
                                                   "children":[  
                                                      {  
                                                         "content":"(And that the universe does.)",
                                                         "children":[  
                                                            {  
                                                               "content":"All is Truth"
                                                            }
                                                         ]
                                                      }
                                                   ]
                                                }
                                             ]
                                          }
                                       ]
                                    }
                                 ]
                              }
                           ]
                        }
                     ]
                  },
                  {  
                     "content":"And that nothing fails its perfect return--",
                     "children":[  
                        {  
                           "content":"lies are perfect returns,"
                        },
                        {  
                           "content":"And henceforth I will go celebrate anything I see or am,",
                           "children":[  
                              {  
                                 "content":"And sing and laugh, and deny nothing."
                              }
                           ]
                        },
                        {  
                           "content":"but grows as inevitably upon itself as the truth does upon  itself"
                        }
                     ]
                  }
               ]
            }
         ]
      }
   ]
}